legs.start_address: Burç, Gazi Cd. No:1, 15200 Burdur Merkez/Burdur, Turkey

steps.html_instructions: At the roundabout, continue straight onto İsmet İnönü Blv.
At the roundabout, take the 2nd exit onto Armağan İlci Blv.

Turn left onto Armağan İlci Blv./D350/D650
Continue to follow D650
Take the exit toward Konya Denizli Yolu
Keep right at the fork to continue toward Afyon Konya Yolu/D300
Keep left and merge onto Afyon Konya Yolu/D300

Turn left onto Eskişehir Konya Yolu/D675
Continue to follow D675
Take the ramp onto Afyon Ankara Yolu/D260/E96

Take the ramp on the left onto Ankara Eskişehir Yolu/D200/D260/E90
Continue to follow D200

Merge onto Ankara Çevre Yolu/O-20/E89/E90 via the ramp to Sincan/Ayaş/İstanbul
Continue to follow Ankara Çevre Yolu/O-20/E89
Keep right at the fork to continue on Ankara Çevre Yolu/O-20, follow signs for İstanbul/D750/Havalimanı/Kırıkkale/Samsun/E88

Continue onto Esenboğa Kavşağı/D140
Continue to follow D140

Slight right onto Çankırı Blv./Çubuk Şabanözü Yolu
Continue to follow Çubuk Şabanözü Yolu
Turn left to stay on Maruf Köyü Yolu
